Limited Liability Company Guide

Limited Liability Company Guide
Get guidance on federal income tax planning and compliance issues, as well as state tax and business law requirements.



Get a Demo
Learn More
Contact a Rep











        Limited Liability Company Guide offers guidance on federal income tax planning and compliance issues, as well as state tax and business law requirements. It provides LLC tax planning guidance and business law preparation, as well as discussions on the dissolution, liquidation and winding up of an LLC.
        
    

Key Features

Get answers to your LLC tax planning questions with ease:

Access easy-to-understand explanations about forming, operating and terminating LLCs, special uses for LLCs, LLC business law and more.
Review explanations that contain numerous examples, practical planning points, cautions and checklists.





Details



Description
Features
Specification




The Limited Liability Company Guide covers specific LLC tax planning topics, including:

Allocations and distributions
Capital structure and contributions
Dissolution and winding up
Estate planning
Forming LLCs/choice of entity
Full text of state LLC laws
Interstate operations
Management and control issues
Members’ limited liability
Mergers and conversions
Special uses of LLCs
State LLC business law summaries
Tax classification of LLCs
Taxation of LLCs and LLC members
Transfer of LLC interests
Uniform Limited Liability Company Act of 1996
Uniform Limited Partnership Act of 2001
Uniform Partnership Act of 1997



The Limited Liability Company Guide is a practice-oriented guide that includes:

Easy-to-understand explanations about forming, operating and terminating LLCs, special uses for LLCs, LLC business law and more.
Monthly planning articles by recognized experts integrated into explanations.
Explanations that contain numerous examples, practical planning points, cautions and checklists.
Code provisions, Committee Reports, Regulations, IRS Rulings and court cases that pertain to LLC tax planning.
State law summaries for partnerships, LLCs and LLPs.
Choice of entity considerations.
Tools such as sample articles of organization and LLC operating agreements.
The LLC Advisor monthly newsletter with expert LLC business law commentaries.


Formats available

CCH® IntelliConnect



